     A            Y1SKMM         2S 0       COLHDG('DELETE DATE MONTH')
     A            Y1SKDD         2S 0       COLHDG('DELETE DATE DAY')
     A            Y1KOYY         4S 0       COLHDG('UPDATE DATE YEAR')
