     A            Y1KOJJ         2S 0       COLHDG('UPDATE TIME  ')
     A            Y1KOFF         2S 0       COLHDG('UPDATE TIME MINUTES')
     A            Y1KONA        10          COLHDG('UPDATE PERSON')
      * * * * * * * DATA KEY ITEM * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
      **
     A            Y1TOKU         4S 0       COLHDG('CUSTOMER CODE')
     A            Y1TMEI        15          COLHDG('CUSTOMER NAME')
     A            Y1DTYY         4S 0       COLHDG('DATA YEAR')
      * * * * * * * SALES DATA COUNT * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
